creator: Kliip Colombia
descriptionHtml:
With a single KliiP you join one of the best transport platforms, which allows you to move around the city in the best vehicles, air-conditioned, comfortable, safe, clean and with trained drivers who offer excellent service.
KliiP is an excellent application that offers the best service with fair rates
How does “KliiP” work?
1. Request your trip, open the application and indicate the place where you are, select which is your destination, as well as what type of vehicle you want: Economic or Premium.
2. Confirm your trip, there is already a driver at your disposal! We will tell you its name, as well as the information of the vehicle and at what distance and time it is from your location.
3. Always know the price of your trip. We will tell you from the beginning how much you should pay for your trip.
4. Receive detailed information about your trip at the end of your service via email.
- It is easy. Furthermore, we guarantee that we will exceed your expectations.
- KliiP will provide its services initially in the city of Cali.
- For us your safety is very important.
- We work hand in hand with taxis in order to have more coverage and allow you to get to your destination on time.
- We have 24/7 support with trained personnel to attend to all your concerns.
As you can see, we beat our competition in many ways. Still not convinced?
Download the app and see for yourself!
At KliiP we love to hear from you.
Email: kliipcali@gmail.com
WhatsApp: 318 8584655 - 302 4328356 - 317 5218260
descriptionShort: Now traveling with "Kliip" is much easier and safer.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: We’ve released a number of features. The Wallet is a built-in payment source that allows customers to pay for the ride quicker. It can be topped up with the card or the top-up codes before the trip and used to pay for the trip later. The Follow my ride feature allows a passenger to share their location during the ride with anyone they trust. The Voice Over feature allows people with visual impairments to easily use the app. The UI was also updated to make the user experience smoother.
